---
title: Teriyaki Prawn Poke Style Bowl with Jasmine Rice, Sugar Snaps and Kiwi Salsa
description: This Teriyaki Prawn Poke Style Bowl  is bursting full of flavours and makes the perfect dinner night option from HelloFresh. Cook up a fresh start!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220922_R06_W44_UK_G3897-11323-10_KB_Main_low-b9d8541b.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/teriyaki-prawn-poke-style-bowl-630e2851da952ef1098cbaaa-d98f7edb.pdf
servings: 2
cuisine: Japanese
nutrition:
  calories: 445 kcal
  fat: 5.5 g
  saturated fat: 1 g
